      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride with plenty of character! This vehicle is in fair condition and has been a reliable companion, showing some honest signs of its journey through life. While there are some cosmetic and mechanical areas that could use a little TLC, it remains a solid choice for anyone looking for a functional and spirited car at a great value. It's perfect for a daily commuter or someone looking to add their own personal touch!",
