    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers reliable transportation for its next owner. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the car shows signs of age with some noticeable cosmetic wear on both the interior and exterior, including minor dings and seat upholstery thinning. It has been regularly maintained, though a few minor non-essential components may require attention soon. This is a solid choice for someone seeking a functional, everyday driver at a sensible price point.",
      "price": 20000.0,
